article.description: Desmond Bane had 30 points as TCU defeated Nebraska 88-72 in the second round of the NIT on Sunday night.
article.headline: Bane scores 30, TCU beats Nebraska 88-72 in NIT
article.linkText: Bane scores 30, TCU beats Nebraska 88-72 in NIT
article.story: FORT WORTH, Texas -- Desmond Bane had 30 points as TCU defeated Nebraska 88-72 in the second round of the NIT on Sunday night. Bane shot 6 for 9 from deep. He added eight rebounds. JD Miller had 15 points and seven rebounds for TCU (22-13). Kendric Davis added 12 points. Kouat Noi had 12 points for the hosts. James Palmer Jr. had 19 points for the Cornhuskers (19-17). Glynn Watson Jr. added 17 points, nine rebounds and six assists. Tanner Borchardt had 16 points and 13 rebounds. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
